[/code]
Save and close that

In client.java

Add this:

[code]public Level Level = new Level(this);[/code]

Now comment out or delete every [code]refreshSkills();[/code]

Now search

[code]int oldLevel = getLevelForXP(playerXP[skill]);
[/code]
above it add

[code]Level.SkillUpdate(skill);[/code]


Enjoy!
